1
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:32,540
[Episode 3]

2
00:01:33,540 --> 00:01:35,900
Have you seen this before?

3
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:40,070
Try to recall the details. This belonged to the deceased.

4
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:41,330
It was found here.

5
00:01:41,339 --> 00:01:43,139
But the content is missing.

6
00:01:43,140 --> 00:01:45,380
I really have no idea.

7
00:01:46,020 --> 00:01:47,560
Let's go.

8
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:05,880
Your Highness, are you all right?

9
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:09,000
Xiao Sha, this is Long Yue.

10
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:15,160
Come with me.

11
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,279
There is a secret passage to the alley.

12
00:02:34,279 --> 00:02:38,220
It's safer for Your Highness to use this exit.

13
00:02:38,220 --> 00:02:41,420
Sir Zhao dropped this pouch just now.

14
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:46,099
If the authorities come for an investigation, be cautious.

15
00:02:46,099 --> 00:02:48,680
Yes, I will handle this matter with caution.

16
00:02:57,740 --> 00:03:00,099
You should know by now this is no simple matter.

17
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:03,880
I understand now why Sir Zhao insisted on meeting you.

18
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,619
The evidence he was holding...

19
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:08,419
would only be useful when it is in your hands, Brother.

20
00:03:08,419 --> 00:03:12,840
Only you can go up against the force behind the case.

21
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:16,460
But sadly, Sir Zhao was killed.

22
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:20,140
We need to find more information on that lady.

23
00:03:20,140 --> 00:03:23,959
Wait, Brother. I thought you were not interested in women.

24
00:03:23,959 --> 00:03:27,400
I noticed just now you had your eyes on her.

25
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:30,860
What's wrong? Are you having feelings for her?

26
00:03:30,860 --> 00:03:33,080
This is very unusual.

27
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:37,210
[Moon Embrace Teahouse]

28
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:43,039
Everyone is waiting in the dining hall.

29
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:46,220
Your Highness, please present yourself in the hall.

30
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,700
What are you doing?

31
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:05,779
I apologize for making such a fuss for you.

32
00:04:05,779 --> 00:04:09,099
But I don't have much of an appetite. Go without me.

33
00:04:09,099 --> 00:04:12,140
Enjoy yourself with The foods heartily.

34
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:16,100
Yes, Your Highness.

35
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:32,359
Your Highness, I was keeping watch outside the room.

36
00:04:32,359 --> 00:04:35,679
I never saw you coming in. How did you get in here?

37
00:04:35,679 --> 00:04:37,139
I was so scared just now.

38
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:39,740
I have Xiao Sha with me, I have my ways.

39
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:39,960
My mother passed away when I was four years old.

40
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:42,059
But Lady Yun took pity on me.

41
00:05:42,059 --> 00:05:45,000
She brought me to the palace and raised me there.

42
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:48,379
I still remember the days I was haunted by nightmares.

43
00:05:48,379 --> 00:05:50,299
I couldn't fall asleep.

44
00:05:50,299 --> 00:05:54,240
It was Lady Yun that kept me company all the time.

45
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:58,540
She played me the song of a vessel flute until I fell asleep.

46
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:07,479
For me, Lady Yun is like a mother to me.

47
00:06:11,540 --> 00:06:16,419
Brother, I know the very sight of me is a nuisance for you.

48
00:06:16,419 --> 00:06:18,799
You felt like I took Lady Yun from you.

49
00:06:18,799 --> 00:06:20,580
You kept ignoring me.

50
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:23,160
But when someone picked on me,

51
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:26,779
the first person that stood up for me... was none other but you.

52
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:35,699
Just because you are bringing up memories... doesn't mean I will help with this investigation.

53
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:40,660
Brother, the culprit is no normal killer.

54
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:45,939
Their identities and background, the authorities have no records on them.

55
00:06:45,939 --> 00:06:49,280
Are we going to let Sir Zhao die in vain?

56
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:56,019
Brother, for the sake of Lady Yun,

57
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:58,200
we can just...

58
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:03,999
Did I say something wrong again?

59
00:07:03,999 --> 00:07:08,319
You have been following me for years. You should know well not to overstep.

60
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:11,779
These are not the matter we should be discussing.

61
00:07:11,779 --> 00:07:13,540
I...

62
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:16,420
I apologize, Brother.

63
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,420
Owl,

64
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:46,450
you could have been soaring in the endless sky.

65
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:50,660
Why did you choose to come back to this palace?

66
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,790
Your Highness.

67
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:12,319
This is the evidence of rank-selling from...

68
00:08:12,319 --> 00:08:15,340
the Crown Prince and Minister of Personnel.

69
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:26,540
Xiao Sha.

70
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:33,659
- Your Highness.
- Do you know... what kind of a person the Crown Prince is?

71
00:08:33,659 --> 00:08:36,879
I heard he is ambitious, cruel, and petty.

72
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:38,179
He is not easy to befriend.

73
00:08:38,180 --> 00:08:40,659
We need to be cautious with people like him.

74
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,220
Yes.

75
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:45,399
Right.

76
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:48,659
I am sure you knew me well before I lost my memories.

77
00:08:48,660 --> 00:08:51,119
His Majesty brought you out to the hut sometimes.

78
00:08:51,119 --> 00:08:52,579
I was always there.

79
00:08:52,580 --> 00:08:55,350
When did you first meet me?

80
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:59,639
I think it was after His Majesty's coronation. I picked you up from the Cold Harem.

81
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:02,779
Was that the first time His Majesty met me?

82
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:04,099
I don't think so.

83
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:07,220
So where did he first meet me?

84
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:11,240
Well...I am not sure either.

85
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:13,499
I may be His Majesty's personal bodyguard,

86
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:16,660
but I can't be around him all the time.

87
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:19,120
You may go now.

88
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:43,159
Your Highness, there is an invitation from the palace.

89
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:45,819
The empress will hold a ball three days from now.

90
00:09:45,819 --> 00:09:47,939
Your Highness is invited.

91
00:09:47,939 --> 00:09:50,779
There is also a list of guests that will be attending.

92
00:09:50,780 --> 00:09:53,100
Please, have a look.

93
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:54,579
Very well.

94
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:58,419
Please reply to Her Majesty for me. I will be at the ball on time.

95
00:09:58,419 --> 00:10:01,280
Yes, I shall go now.

96
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,770
Your Highness.

97
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:17,300
[Attendance List]

98
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:21,799
Your Highness, Prince Li's name is on the list.

99
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:25,299
Her Majesty is aiming to matchmake you and Prince Li?

100
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:29,720
But why are so many other strangers invited as well?

101
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:33,600
Xiao Sha, do you know the names on this list?

102
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:39,340
These are princes that are yet to be married.

103
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:41,259
Matchmaking me with Prince Li?

104
00:10:41,260 --> 00:10:44,860
It might as well be a blind date for me and the princes.

105
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:48,459
Your Highness, maybe His Majesty thinks Prince Li refuses to marry?

106
00:10:48,459 --> 00:10:51,500
Is that why they are holding this blind date?

107
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:55,919
Wait! What do they take us for? It's not like anyone can marry a princess.

108
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:59,759
Your Highness, this ball is being held by the empress.

109
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:01,859
I cannot enter the inner palace.

110
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:04,620
Please, watch your back.

111
00:11:05,620 --> 00:11:09,619
If Prince Li is not around, I doubt the others would dare to disrespect me.

112
00:11:09,619 --> 00:11:11,599
Why wouldn't Prince Li be there?

113
00:11:11,599 --> 00:11:16,199
His name is on the list, but he might not attend the ball.

114
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:45,659
Princess!

115
00:11:45,659 --> 00:11:48,219
- Stop following me, okay?
- Princess!

116
00:11:48,219 --> 00:11:50,139
You wouldn't go to the lake with me.

117
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:52,859
You are not interested in flower viewing either.

118
00:11:52,860 --> 00:11:55,079
Princess, do you think I don't deserve you?

119
00:11:55,079 --> 00:11:58,579
I simply don't want to be with you. Can you please stop bothering me?

120
00:11:58,579 --> 00:12:01,100
Princess!

121
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:03,340
Princess! Stop!

122
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:06,980
Who is that?

123
00:12:07,740 --> 00:12:09,779
Your Highness.

124
00:12:09,779 --> 00:12:12,539
The elder son of Prince Qing He and Princess Zhao Yun.

125
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:15,859
You should know, Princess Zhao Yun grew up without parents.

126
00:12:15,859 --> 00:12:20,339
She has no siblings either. So she is living with her uncle for the time being.

127
00:12:20,339 --> 00:12:21,939
You have nothing to be so arrogant about.

128
00:12:21,940 --> 00:12:24,519
You are just an orphan that lives under other's care.

129
00:12:24,519 --> 00:12:26,950
You should be grateful I am even laying my eyes on you.

130
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,440
I am warning you, let go of me!

131
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,870
I am letting you go. Try me!

132
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:38,279
I will tell Brother Wuyou and let him finish you!

133
00:12:38,279 --> 00:12:39,819
You are bringing up Prince Li now?

134
00:12:39,820 --> 00:12:42,239
But he never attends to events like this.

135
00:12:42,239 --> 00:12:44,300
You are not going to see him.

136
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:49,999
How dare you push me!

137
00:12:49,999 --> 00:12:51,600
Stop right there!

138
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:54,480
Sister, save me!

139
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:57,259
Your Highness, this is Princess Rong Le from Qi.

140
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:58,860
Scram!

141
00:12:59,560 --> 00:13:03,479
I was wondering who was here. It's the hideous Princess of Qi.

142
00:13:03,479 --> 00:13:05,840
No wonder she is so nosy.

143
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,370
I heard Prince Li abandoned you.

144
00:13:07,370 --> 00:13:10,630
So you want one of us to marry you instead.

145
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:12,739
Fat chance.

146
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:16,600
Listen! Even though I am not going to marry anyone,

147
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:19,680
I would never marry someone that was dumped and hideous.

148
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:21,959
I thought only Prince Li behaved in this manner.

149
00:13:21,959 --> 00:13:24,979
I never thought the elder son of Prince Qing He was this bold as well.

150
00:13:24,979 --> 00:13:29,779
I can say whatever I want! I am taking off that mask to show your hideous look!

151
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:43,180
Nicely done, Princess Rong Le! He deserved this!

152
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:54,660
Brother Wuyou, you are here.

153
00:14:07,580 --> 00:14:10,000
Prince Li?

154
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,400
What did you say just now?

155
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:14,340
Nothing, I said nothing.

156
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:19,199
I said... if Prince Li doesn't like this woman,

157
00:14:19,199 --> 00:14:22,500
I would never marry her.

158
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:26,379
- If this is the woman my brother likes, you would marry her?
- No!

159
00:14:26,379 --> 00:14:29,359
No, that's not what I meant. What I meant was...

160
00:14:29,359 --> 00:14:33,099
I won't marry her whetherPrince Li likes her or not.

161
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,899
You might as well be a eunuch then.

162
00:14:36,100 --> 00:14:37,900
No!

163
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:40,519
Get lost.

164
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:43,320
- Guards, take him away.
- Yes.

165
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:45,479
I am here by the order of the empress.

166
00:14:45,479 --> 00:14:47,959
- Get up!
- You can't take me by force!

167
00:14:47,959 --> 00:14:49,979
- You can't do this to me!
- Prince Qing He had a son at an old age.

168
00:14:49,979 --> 00:14:51,959
- He spoils his son a lot.
- Let go of me!

169
00:14:51,959 --> 00:14:55,359
He lets him do anything. He is even bold enough to cause trouble here.

170
00:14:55,359 --> 00:14:57,079
He should have known his place here.

171
00:14:57,079 --> 00:14:58,979
I am glad Brother Wuyou was here.

172
00:14:58,979 --> 00:15:02,480
Otherwise, Princess Rong Le would have been caught up in this.

173
00:15:03,260 --> 00:15:07,479
Speaking of you... You know he is a scoundrel, why did you mess with him?

174
00:15:07,479 --> 00:15:09,279
I didn't mess with him.

175
00:15:09,279 --> 00:15:11,319
He kept bothering me.

176
00:15:11,319 --> 00:15:13,279
If I were to have martial art skills like Princess Rong Le,

177
00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:16,260
I would have beaten him to a pulp.

178
00:15:16,260 --> 00:15:20,140
Princess of Qi actually knows martial arts.

179
00:15:20,140 --> 00:15:22,579
There are two things Prince Li never does.

180
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:27,159
He never drinks. He never touches a woman.

181
00:15:27,159 --> 00:15:29,700
Who says a princess cannot learn martial arts?

182
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:32,139
If Your Highness wishes to know more about me,

183
00:15:32,140 --> 00:15:36,720
you will learn that I know more than just martial arts.

184
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,599
Your Highness is willing to attend the ball.

185
00:15:38,599 --> 00:15:42,540
It means you do have some interest in me.

186
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:46,999
Why don't you come to the ball with me?

187
00:15:46,999 --> 00:15:50,280
The empress arrives!

188
00:15:55,900 --> 00:16:00,859
- All hail the Her Majesty.
- At ease, all of you.

189
00:16:00,859 --> 00:16:03,360
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Mother.

190
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:09,539
I have heard rumors about how talented the princess is.

191
00:16:09,540 --> 00:16:13,280
It seems to be true from what I saw.

192
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:15,519
Please, I don't deserve the praise.

193
00:16:15,519 --> 00:16:19,499
Prince Li is here. Come to the ball before you leave.

194
00:16:19,499 --> 00:16:24,519
Coincidently, Ya Li is here with us today.

195
00:16:24,519 --> 00:16:28,339
I am the daughter of the Central Secretary, Ya Li. Greetings, Princess of Qi,

196
00:16:28,339 --> 00:16:31,980
Prince Li, Prince Chen, and Princess Zhao Yun.

197
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,899
I have matters I must see to.

198
00:16:42,899 --> 00:16:44,780
So long.

199
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,659
It's almost time for the death anniversary of Lady Yun.

200
00:16:50,660 --> 00:16:53,960
My brother needs to retrieve some belongings of hers.

201
00:16:55,300 --> 00:16:57,199
He does it every year.

202
00:16:57,199 --> 00:16:59,620
A filial son indeed.

203
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:02,179
Since Prince Li is not coming with us,

204
00:17:02,180 --> 00:17:05,280
Wuyu, you shall go in his place.

205
00:17:29,060 --> 00:17:32,180
Come, have a toast.

206
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:43,199
Princess, you came a long way.

207
00:17:43,199 --> 00:17:45,139
His Majesty was concerned the welcome was not decent enough.

208
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:48,059
I was ordered to hold this feast for you.

209
00:17:48,060 --> 00:17:50,939
All the guests are about your age.

210
00:17:50,940 --> 00:17:53,459
I hope you won't feel awkward here.

211
00:17:53,460 --> 00:17:56,440
Thank you to His Majesty and Your Majesty.

212
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:58,159
Your have never been to our nation before.

213
00:17:58,159 --> 00:18:01,900
How is your life at the manor?

214
00:18:01,900 --> 00:18:05,540
His Majesty arranged a modest manor for me.

215
00:18:06,700 --> 00:18:09,219
- However...
- What is wrong?

216
00:18:09,219 --> 00:18:11,579
Are the servants not attentive enough?

217
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:15,179
If so, I can arrange to get the other servants for you.

218
00:18:15,180 --> 00:18:17,539
I need to ensure you are having a good time here.

219
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:18,979
Your Majesty misunderstood.

220
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:22,219
The servants are taking good care of me.

221
00:18:22,220 --> 00:18:25,480
Perhaps they are taking care of me all too well.

222
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:29,019
I wish to see the view of the capital.

223
00:18:29,020 --> 00:18:30,780
But that seems impossible.

224
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:36,059
Why? Is someone stopping you from leaving the palace?

225
00:18:36,059 --> 00:18:37,739
That is not the case.

226
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:41,579
Every time I try to leave, all the guards come along.

227
00:18:41,579 --> 00:18:44,739
It's too high-profile, I feel concerned about this.

228
00:18:44,740 --> 00:18:48,080
Which is why I can't go out.

229
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:51,740
They simply wish to ensure your safety.

230
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:53,779
But I already have a personal bodyguard.

231
00:18:53,779 --> 00:18:58,580
He was sent by my brother before I came here.

232
00:18:58,580 --> 00:18:59,819
I see.

233
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:03,899
Well, I shall send the order.

234
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:06,719
From now on, you may leave the palace as you please.

235
00:19:06,719 --> 00:19:10,340
All the guards need not follow you.

236
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:12,360
Much obliged, Your Majesty.

237
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:15,280
Princess, enjoy yourself.

238
00:19:17,460 --> 00:19:21,260
Make yourself at home. Enjoy the food.

239
00:19:21,879 --> 00:19:23,720
To your health.

240
00:19:28,980 --> 00:19:32,679
Prince Chen, all you care about is the food.

241
00:19:32,679 --> 00:19:35,360
What about the princess?

242
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:40,400
But I am not Wuyou.

243
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,939
I wouldn't expect anything from Prince Li.

244
00:19:42,940 --> 00:19:46,659
But if Prince Chen is here, I do have some expectations.

245
00:19:48,140 --> 00:19:50,660
What do you expect from me?

246
00:19:50,660 --> 00:19:55,119
I heard rumors about... how subtle and dapper you are.

247
00:19:55,119 --> 00:19:57,019
You know how to care for a lady.

248
00:19:57,020 --> 00:20:00,159
If I could have your attention and care,

249
00:20:00,159 --> 00:20:04,040
my life in Northern Lin might be more interesting.

250
00:20:05,660 --> 00:20:07,499
Indeed!

251
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:10,659
Prince Chen knows what's best for a lady.

252
00:20:10,660 --> 00:20:14,139
Should you ever need any help on any matter,

253
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:16,460
you can always ask for his help.

254
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:19,140
Your Majesty, this is just...

255
00:20:22,620 --> 00:20:24,439
Princess Rong Le,

256
00:20:24,439 --> 00:20:26,960
Wuyu is simply unreliable.

257
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:31,839
Brother Wuyou is a good man. Do not fall for the rumors.

258
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:38,180
Princess, I wonder what hobby you have?

259
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:42,919
Your Majesty.

260
00:20:42,919 --> 00:20:46,099
I don't really have any interest in particular.

261
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:50,839
However, I do love tea.

262
00:20:54,820 --> 00:20:58,730
I wonder what Prince Chen does in his free time?

263
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:01,680
Well,

264
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:06,479
I love to visit the public houses. (Brothels)

265
00:21:06,479 --> 00:21:10,479
What are the odds? I went to some places in my homeland.

266
00:21:10,479 --> 00:21:12,639
But I have never been to a public house.

267
00:21:12,639 --> 00:21:17,119
I wonder if Prince Chen has the time... to show me around the public house?

268
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:23,539
Are you even a woman?

269
00:21:23,539 --> 00:21:25,879
You actually want to see a public house?

270
00:21:25,879 --> 00:21:28,719
My intention is not about the public house.

271
00:21:28,719 --> 00:21:32,739
I just want a chance to know you better.

272
00:21:32,739 --> 00:21:37,540
I wish to find out what kind of lady do you like.

273
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:44,519
Mother, pardon me but I am feeling unwell.

274
00:21:44,519 --> 00:21:46,860
I must be on my way now.

275
00:21:49,560 --> 00:21:51,620
Little brat.

276
00:21:53,840 --> 00:21:57,199
Princess, make yourself at home.

277
00:21:57,199 --> 00:21:59,400
Same goes for everyone.

278
00:22:34,170 --> 00:22:36,740
Your Highness.

279
00:22:36,740 --> 00:22:42,120
Perhaps His Majesty is going to let Prince Li marry the princess.

280
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:44,430
I thought we had another six months.

281
00:22:44,430 --> 00:22:46,370
Even if that is my father's plan,

282
00:22:46,370 --> 00:22:49,620
there is nothing my father can do if she refuses to get married.

283
00:22:49,620 --> 00:22:53,599
Your Highness must know, Her Majesty held a feast recently.

284
00:22:53,599 --> 00:22:56,099
The princess showed her liking to Prince Chen.

285
00:22:56,100 --> 00:22:58,219
Prince Chen and Li are inseparable.

286
00:22:58,220 --> 00:23:01,979
If Prince Chen marries her, it would be just like Prince Li married her.

287
00:23:01,979 --> 00:23:04,560
Your Highness, we cannot let our guard down.

288
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:06,510
She is but a mere princess.

289
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:08,670
There is no way she is a threat to me.

290
00:23:08,679 --> 00:23:11,699
Besides, judging from Wuyu's temper,

291
00:23:11,700 --> 00:23:14,880
if he really does marry that roguish princess,

292
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:17,580
that could be a great show to enjoy.

293
00:23:17,580 --> 00:23:22,799
Your Highness, do you know Prince Li is investigating the case of rank-selling?

294
00:23:28,420 --> 00:23:31,559
I thought no one knew? How did he find out?

295
00:23:31,559 --> 00:23:33,460
A snitch told Prince Li.

296
00:23:33,460 --> 00:23:36,020
But rest assured, I came prepared.

297
00:23:36,020 --> 00:23:37,939
The snitch is no longer with us.

298
00:23:37,940 --> 00:23:40,739
But we can see just how ambitious Prince Li is.

299
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:42,299
We can't afford to get sloppy.

300
00:23:42,300 --> 00:23:46,099
Wuyou is always carefree and a man of seclusion.

301
00:23:46,100 --> 00:23:48,660
He tricked me into trusting him.

302
00:23:49,540 --> 00:23:51,899
But he is actually plotting against me.

303
00:23:51,900 --> 00:23:54,500
Calm down, Your Highness.

304
00:23:54,500 --> 00:23:59,019
What we must do now is to stop Prince Li from expanding his influence.

305
00:23:59,019 --> 00:24:02,819
The order for the marriage is yet to arrive. It's not too late for us.

306
00:24:02,819 --> 00:24:04,579
You mean...

307
00:24:04,580 --> 00:24:06,720
Your Highness is already married.

308
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:08,619
Marrying the princess is not possible.

309
00:24:08,620 --> 00:24:11,940
Unless, we make her...

310
00:24:12,740 --> 00:24:14,739
married to one of us.

311
00:24:14,740 --> 00:24:17,240
My father won't agree with this.

312
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:19,300
Unless...

313
00:24:26,340 --> 00:24:31,419
Not only is Princess Rong Le hideous, but her behavior is also even more surprising.

314
00:24:31,419 --> 00:24:34,820
She asked to visit the public house with me while Her Majesty was there.

315
00:24:34,820 --> 00:24:38,479
Wuyou, why would a lady even act like she did?

316
00:24:38,479 --> 00:24:40,299
Isn't that great?

317
00:24:40,300 --> 00:24:43,019
You don't need to visit the public house on your own.

318
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:45,179
You can bring your wife along.

319
00:24:45,180 --> 00:24:47,019
A couple sharing the same interest.

320
00:24:47,020 --> 00:24:49,940
That could be a great tale for us.

321
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:53,840
Wuyou, stop making fun of me.

322
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:58,420
Don't you think something is fishy?

323
00:24:59,500 --> 00:25:03,920
She was into you just moments ago,

324
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:07,880
and now she got her eyes on me instead?

325
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:11,080
Something is not right about this.

326
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:14,500
A conspiracy, something is at miss.

327
00:25:15,380 --> 00:25:18,840
If you know she is planning something, why bother worrying?

328
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:22,080
I am being cautious.

329
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:24,979
I may not be as good-looking as you,

330
00:25:24,980 --> 00:25:29,240
but at least I am subtle and dapper, chivalrous, and a gentleman.

331
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:32,460
Did she really fall for me?

332
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,120
Brother?

333
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:36,740
Brother!

334
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:43,980
Time flies like an arrow.

335
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:48,860
Even Yali is of age to get a husband now.

336
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:51,859
So, your father is Wuyou's teacher.

337
00:25:51,860 --> 00:25:56,059
You were a childhood friend of Wuyou. You are meant for each other.

338
00:25:56,059 --> 00:25:57,260
What a shame.

339
00:25:57,260 --> 00:26:01,460
Your Majesty, I don't deserve Prince Li.

340
00:26:02,620 --> 00:26:07,619
It's the emperor's decision. The princess is in our land.

341
00:26:07,619 --> 00:26:12,199
They may not be married yet, but the marriage agreement still stands.

342
00:26:12,820 --> 00:26:17,659
Yali, what is your plan now?

343
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:19,779
I am still too young.

344
00:26:19,780 --> 00:26:22,740
I just want to spend more time with my father.

345
00:26:22,740 --> 00:26:25,020
I don't wish to plan for a marriage yet.

346
00:26:25,020 --> 00:26:28,899
You may not be in a hurry, but I am concerned.

347
00:26:28,899 --> 00:26:32,099
Your mother was like a sister to me.

348
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:36,859
If you ever find someone you love, you must let me know.

349
00:26:36,859 --> 00:26:38,930
I will be your witness.

350
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:43,100
Yes, thank you, Your Majesty.

351
00:26:43,100 --> 00:26:45,259
You have always been an obedient child.

352
00:26:45,260 --> 00:26:50,199
Perhaps too obedient. You might run into trouble someday.

353
00:26:51,170 --> 00:26:54,140
[Rather Peaceful, Elegant Home]

354
00:26:54,140 --> 00:26:56,139
Your Highness.

355
00:26:56,140 --> 00:26:57,620
I am leaving.

356
00:26:57,620 --> 00:26:59,899
Do you need the guards with you?

357
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:01,940
No.

358
00:27:01,940 --> 00:27:03,939
I am sure you all know about Her Majesty's order.

359
00:27:03,940 --> 00:27:07,139
From now on, I don't need the guards to follow me.

360
00:27:07,139 --> 00:27:08,979
I have Xiao Sha to protect me.

361
00:27:08,980 --> 00:27:10,450
Yes.

362
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:21,459
Is there anything else?

363
00:27:21,460 --> 00:27:24,280
I must come along to ensure your safety.

364
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:26,659
Sending guards may be too high-profile.

365
00:27:26,660 --> 00:27:29,619
If it's just me, it won't draw as much attention.

366
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:31,659
I grew up in Zhongshan.

367
00:27:31,660 --> 00:27:34,320
If there is anything great on the street, I know all about them.

368
00:27:34,320 --> 00:27:36,540
I am not going out now.

369
00:27:36,540 --> 00:27:38,290
Back to the room.

370
00:27:38,290 --> 00:27:41,970
[The Waves Are to be Heard Quickly]

371
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:55,180
I knew you were here.

372
00:27:55,180 --> 00:27:59,940
Why? Are you still upset about what happened back there?

373
00:28:01,340 --> 00:28:05,819
You'll see, Wuyou and I will teach that son of Prince Qing He a lesson.

374
00:28:05,820 --> 00:28:07,460
How dare he bully you.

375
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:10,100
No, I know.

376
00:28:10,100 --> 00:28:13,579
As long as you and Brother Wuyou are here, no one would dare bully me.

377
00:28:13,579 --> 00:28:18,620
Besides, I have Princess Rong Le to back me up now.

378
00:28:18,620 --> 00:28:22,120
The princess? Don't be so naive, okay?

379
00:28:22,120 --> 00:28:26,619
Haven't you heard? Not only is she ugly, but she also has a foul temper too!

380
00:28:26,619 --> 00:28:28,200
Of course not!

381
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:30,770
Your heart brings about appearance.

382
00:28:30,770 --> 00:28:32,770
She is so kind, she can't be ugly.

383
00:28:32,779 --> 00:28:37,139
When I first met her, I felt like she is very friendly.

384
00:28:37,139 --> 00:28:41,739
But I don't get it. Why would Wuyou refuse to marry her?

385
00:28:41,739 --> 00:28:43,819
What could you possibly understand?

386
00:28:43,820 --> 00:28:45,859
Wuyou was too protective of you.

387
00:28:45,860 --> 00:28:48,600
It made you naive and simple-minded.

388
00:28:48,660 --> 00:28:50,260
You should just listen to me.

389
00:28:50,260 --> 00:28:52,710
Stay away from all troubles. Okay?

390
00:28:52,719 --> 00:28:55,699
What? You are no better than me!

391
00:28:55,700 --> 00:28:59,919
All you ever know is to have fun. How dare you lecture me!

392
00:28:59,919 --> 00:29:02,259
Princess Rong Le humiliated you in front of everyone,

393
00:29:02,259 --> 00:29:05,440
I like her even more now!

394
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:09,260
You...

395
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:20,740
Madam Qiu, I heard you came from Zhongshan.

396
00:29:20,740 --> 00:29:22,640
Master Xiao, how may I help you?

397
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:27,840
I heard Zhongshan is a land full of beauties.

398
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:34,159
Princess? They say the dairy cake of Zhongshan is delicious.

399
00:29:34,159 --> 00:29:36,980
Let me get you some from the market.

400
00:29:44,460 --> 00:29:46,460
Beauty...

401
00:29:52,220 --> 00:29:53,859
I have never seen one.

402
00:29:53,860 --> 00:29:56,220
But I did see a lot of ugly ladies.

403
00:29:57,940 --> 00:29:59,720
But...

404
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:10,699
Master Xiao, why are you leaving again?

405
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:12,380
I am...

406
00:30:13,740 --> 00:30:16,100
Why is your face all red?

407
00:30:17,530 --> 00:30:19,140
[House of Fragrance]

408
00:30:19,140 --> 00:30:20,739
Sorry for the long wait, Master Chen.

409
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:24,099
- This way, please.
- Ladies, bring out the wine!

410
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:27,339
Master Chang, how do you like the lady?

411
00:30:27,340 --> 00:30:30,100
Not bad.

412
00:30:32,420 --> 00:30:34,779
Look at this handsome young man.

413
00:30:34,780 --> 00:30:39,880
You are so striking that all our ladies are outshined!

414
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:43,320
Madam, I wish to see Miss Chen Yu.

415
00:30:44,620 --> 00:30:47,160
Please, make this arrangement for me.

416
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:52,780
Unfortunately, Chen Yu is being reserved by those gentlemen.

417
00:30:53,620 --> 00:30:55,200
Come.

418
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:02,000
Let's go upstairs.

419
00:31:03,180 --> 00:31:05,420
Come.

420
00:31:09,500 --> 00:31:13,080
I thought he doesn't touch wine and women.

421
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:16,420
Those gentlemen are here for Miss Chen Yu, too?

422
00:31:16,420 --> 00:31:20,820
After all, Miss Chen Yu is one of the kind here.

423
00:31:20,820 --> 00:31:24,099
Madam, I simply ask for Miss Chen Yu to play a song for me.

424
00:31:24,099 --> 00:31:26,080
It won't take up too much time.

425
00:31:27,340 --> 00:31:28,880
Well...

426
00:31:35,460 --> 00:31:37,779
Sure, not a problem at all.

427
00:31:37,780 --> 00:31:42,019
I will send Miss Chen Yu to your room first.

428
00:31:42,020 --> 00:31:45,459
Then, I will send her to the next room.

429
00:31:45,500 --> 00:31:49,900
As for the other gentlemen, they did pay for her.

430
00:31:49,940 --> 00:31:52,239
I can't possibly disrespect them. Right?

431
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:09,899
Greetings, sir.

432
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:12,219
I have heard about how gorgeous and beautiful you are.

433
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:15,439
Now that I have met you, the words are true.

434
00:32:15,439 --> 00:32:17,219
Much appreciated, sir.

435
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:19,860
You are quite the gentleman yourself.

436
00:32:26,260 --> 00:32:29,420
I am not here to seek pleasure.

437
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:33,080
I simply wish to strike a deal with you.

438
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:36,840
Sir, I doubt I am the right person.

439
00:32:36,840 --> 00:32:38,939
I am but a humble courtesan.

440
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:41,660
Why would you need me for a business deal?

441
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:49,519
Sixteen years ago, there was a local officer.

442
00:32:49,519 --> 00:32:51,619
He was involved in Qin Yong's mutiny.

443
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:53,379
His whole family was executed.

444
00:32:53,380 --> 00:32:56,140
A total of 79 family members were killed.

445
00:32:56,140 --> 00:33:00,719
But when the bodies were sent in for autopsy, one body was missing.

446
00:33:00,719 --> 00:33:04,759
I heard the missing body... belonged to the youngest daughter.

447
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:10,379
His family name is Yu.

448
00:33:10,380 --> 00:33:13,420
Her daughter was born in the morning.

449
00:33:13,420 --> 00:33:16,779
As the sun rose, the child was born.

450
00:33:16,780 --> 00:33:19,840
He gave her the name Yu Cheng, meaning morning.

451
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:24,300
Chen Yu...

452
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:26,520
Yu Chen.

453
00:33:28,500 --> 00:33:30,940
I don't know what you are talking about.

454
00:33:31,980 --> 00:33:34,120
I am sure you understand.

455
00:33:34,120 --> 00:33:38,199
If I can find out about this, so can the others.

456
00:33:38,199 --> 00:33:41,680
Don't you fear for your own safety?

457
00:33:44,340 --> 00:33:49,379
If I mean you harm, I wouldn't bother with the explanation.

458
00:33:49,379 --> 00:33:51,540
What do you want from me?

459
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:56,259
Miss, calm down.

460
00:33:56,260 --> 00:34:00,540
I am not telling you this to threaten you.

461
00:34:02,220 --> 00:34:05,080
I am seeking the truth of the past.

462
00:34:05,080 --> 00:34:09,640
As for your compensation, name any price you want.

463
00:34:16,100 --> 00:34:19,539
What if I tell you... I want to leave this place?

464
00:34:19,539 --> 00:34:22,220
Can you make it happen?

465
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:26,199
If this is your wish, I shall try my best.

466
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:28,900
Madam Qin's greed knows no bounds.

467
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:31,100
She won't let me leave.

468
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:36,220
Unless... your status is even more prominent than her mastermind.

469
00:34:36,220 --> 00:34:37,519
Mastermind?

470
00:34:37,519 --> 00:34:41,600
Man above all, all but one.

471
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:44,340
It's the crown prince?

472
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:46,419
Miss Chen Yu, the guest is asking for you.

473
00:34:46,420 --> 00:34:48,040
Fine.

474
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:51,600
I don't think you can help me.

475
00:34:54,140 --> 00:34:56,120
So long.

476
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:58,560
Will you put your faith in me for once?

477
00:34:58,560 --> 00:35:02,800
I have a plan to get you out of here today.

478
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:04,700
Are you serious about this?

479
00:35:10,200 --> 00:35:12,419
Wuyou, the girl I am fond of...

480
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:14,859
is skilled in instruments and dance, elegant and gorgeous.

481
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:17,099
She may not have a noble status,

482
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:20,820
but she is more innocent than most noble women.

483
00:35:36,180 --> 00:35:37,819
I apologize for the long wait.

484
00:35:37,820 --> 00:35:40,700
I am sorry for my tardiness.

485
00:35:40,700 --> 00:35:43,579
As a token of apology, I shall present you a dance.

486
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:45,980
Would you like that?

487
00:35:45,980 --> 00:35:48,000
The rest of you can leave now.

488
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:54,339
Chen Yu, I have never seen you dance before.

489
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:57,760
I get to witness it thanks to my brother here.

490
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:44,660
While you are dancing, approach the man with the green outfit.

491
00:36:44,660 --> 00:36:47,299
You might get hurt, but not killed.

492
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:49,340
Leave the rest to me.

493
00:37:11,180 --> 00:37:13,220
Help!

494
00:37:14,740 --> 00:37:16,299
Help!

495
00:37:16,300 --> 00:37:19,880
Help! Madam, help me!

496
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:24,740
Leng Yan, stop!

497
00:37:26,180 --> 00:37:28,739
Who dare hurt my precious baby?

498
00:37:28,740 --> 00:37:32,460
Tell me who did this. I will settle this for you.

499
00:37:32,460 --> 00:37:34,840
How are you going to settle this?

500
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:37,139
Wuyou, just show some mercy.

501
00:37:37,140 --> 00:37:40,260
She might not have meant it.

502
00:37:40,260 --> 00:37:44,019
Did my girl do something to offend you?

503
00:37:44,020 --> 00:37:48,540
Chen Yu is the best we have here.

504
00:37:48,540 --> 00:37:54,140
The hands she used to play the chords with are priceless!

505
00:37:54,140 --> 00:37:58,300
What if her priceless hands are exactly what I want?

506
00:37:59,220 --> 00:38:01,539
What did she do to you?

507
00:38:01,540 --> 00:38:05,580
Why would you want to cut her hands off?

508
00:38:05,580 --> 00:38:08,819
I accidentally touched Prince Li's shoulder.

509
00:38:08,820 --> 00:38:11,840
Prince Li? Kneel!

510
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:14,640
You doomed me this time!

511
00:38:14,640 --> 00:38:16,699
Please, show some mercy.

512
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:19,200
The House of Fragrance is a big family,

513
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:22,139
we rely on her hands for livelihood.

514
00:38:22,139 --> 00:38:24,980
Chen Yu, how did you find out who we are?

515
00:38:24,980 --> 00:38:27,939
I can tell you are no commoner, you look chivalrous.

516
00:38:27,940 --> 00:38:30,240
I know what I see.

517
00:38:30,240 --> 00:38:34,139
Your Highness refused to let us know, I wouldn't dare to speculate your identity.

518
00:38:34,139 --> 00:38:36,960
But His Highness called you Wuyou.

519
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:39,059
I am certain you are Prince Li.

520
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:40,979
It was a careless mistake of mine.

521
00:38:40,980 --> 00:38:43,960
I hope Prince Chen can save my life.

522
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,259
- Leng Yan.
- Yes!

523
00:38:45,260 --> 00:38:47,440
I want her out of my sight.

524
00:38:47,440 --> 00:38:49,810
- Brother!
- Stop!

525
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:56,540
I think I have met you somewhere.

526
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:02,980
Can we speak in private?

527
00:39:02,980 --> 00:39:05,060
Teahouse owner?

528
00:39:13,780 --> 00:39:18,359
Madam Qiu, the princess is resting. Please, do not bother her.

529
00:39:18,359 --> 00:39:23,679
Captain Xiao. I am here... to send the medicine.

530
00:39:28,940 --> 00:39:31,379
Madam Qiu, the princess is not feeling well.

531
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:35,080
If someone bothers her and she seeks to blame me...

532
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,859
I will keep this soup warm.

533
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:40,360
She can have it when she is awake.

534
00:39:46,940 --> 00:39:48,859
She wanted to go out this morning.

535
00:39:48,860 --> 00:39:50,899
But she hasn't stepped outside the room.

536
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:52,840
She is not making a sound either.

537
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:57,780
She is gone. Madam Qiu is gone.

538
00:40:03,260 --> 00:40:05,619
It's getting late. Why isn't Her Highness back yet?

539
00:40:05,620 --> 00:40:06,980
You are right.

540
00:40:06,980 --> 00:40:08,620
Did something happen to her?

541
00:40:08,620 --> 00:40:10,739
Should we send Brother Xiao to check on her?

542
00:40:10,740 --> 00:40:14,659
No, Master Xiao is her bodyguard, he can't leave his post.

543
00:40:14,660 --> 00:40:17,840
Madam Qiu is keeping watch on us outside.

544
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:22,919
If he leaves now, they will find out the princess has sneaked out.

545
00:40:22,919 --> 00:40:25,540
The people here will take it wrong.

546
00:40:26,620 --> 00:40:28,259
What do we do now?

547
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:30,399
I just told everyone in the manor.

548
00:40:30,399 --> 00:40:33,600
The princess is not feeling well and she needs to rest.

549
00:40:33,600 --> 00:40:37,280
Yes, fortune favors her. I am sure she will be fine.

550
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:38,779
Right, Lian Xin.

551
00:40:38,780 --> 00:40:42,179
Her Highness has had headaches ever since she got amnesia.

552
00:40:42,180 --> 00:40:44,879
She had a headache around this time last month.

553
00:40:44,879 --> 00:40:48,219
It's almost time. Hurry up and prepare the medicine for Her Highness.

554
00:40:48,219 --> 00:40:52,359
Keep an eye on it. Remember, do not let anyone else touch the medicine.

555
00:40:52,359 --> 00:40:55,560
- Is that clear?
- Okay, I should get going.

556
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:59,819
I will be guarding outside.

557
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:01,819
Leng Yue, keep acting like the princess.

558
00:41:01,820 --> 00:41:04,640
Remember not to move around or talk to anyone.

559
00:41:09,540 --> 00:41:10,900
You have keen sight.

560
00:41:10,900 --> 00:41:14,000
I am Man Yao, the young owner of Moon Embrace Teahouse.

561
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:16,820
I didn't recognize you that day.

562
00:41:16,820 --> 00:41:19,300
