567
00:41:36,300 --> 00:41:41,399
May I ask, is this enough to save Chen Yu's life?

568
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:48,859
Wuyou, this really is a letter from Sir Zhao.

569
00:41:49,940 --> 00:41:52,700
