570
00:41:52,700 --> 00:41:54,299
When you left that day,

571
00:41:54,300 --> 00:41:56,420
I thought the room needed to be cleansed of bad luck,

572
00:41:56,420 --> 00:41:58,699
so I ordered some men to renovate the private room.

573
00:41:58,700 --> 00:42:01,140
I found this in the wall.

574
00:42:01,140 --> 00:42:03,980
I thought the deceased might have left it there.

575
00:42:03,980 --> 00:42:06,440
