579
00:42:24,020 --> 00:42:26,059
I wish to pay for her deed.

580
00:42:26,060 --> 00:42:29,579
I was planning on appointing her as a musician in my teahouse.

581
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:31,699
I want my teahouse to be known by the world.

582
00:42:31,700 --> 00:42:35,099
Miss Chen Yu has beautiful music and looks.

583
00:42:35,100 --> 00:42:37,540
There is no better option other than her.

584
00:42:37,540 --> 00:42:40,320
